#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Z-5 Heavy"
msgid_plural "Z-5 Heavy"
msgstr[0] "Z-5 重型"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Z-5 Heavy is described as 'Powerful machine gun ideal for suppressing enemy positions.' produced by <info>Z-Arm Tech</info>\n"
"the Z-5 Heavy is based on Stone LMG 96. Its ammo box is appeared to be fed from the right side, mirrored to most real-life LMGs. However, this makes Z-5 look like another real-life MG called Stoner LMG 86. It has the word 'Z-5' on its cover latch. It has scratches & some duct tape wrapped over its stock and foregrip, which means this gun is under bad condition but still usable.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <bad>poorly made</bad> and will <bad>easily malfunction</bad> and will <bad>not handle much if any beating</bad>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"Z-5 重型被描述為“壓制敵方陣地的理想強力機槍”，由<info>Z-Arm Tech</info>生產。\n"
"Z-5 重型基於Stone LMG 96。其彈匣似乎從右側供彈，與大多數現實中的輕機槍鏡像。然而，這使得Z-5看起來像另一款現實中的機槍Stoner LMG 86。其蓋鎖上刻有“Z-5”字樣。槍托和前握把上有劃痕並纏著一些膠帶，這意味著這把槍狀況不佳但仍可使用。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<bad>做工粗糙</bad>，<bad>容易發生故障</bad>，並且<bad>經不起多少磕碰</bad>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模組內容</info>"

