msgid_plural "Fixed Z-2 LMPs"
msgstr[0] "修復版 Z-2 LMP"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Z-2 LMP is a <info>small caliber</info> SMG ideal for fast movement and maneuverability produced by <info>Z-Arm Tech</info>.\n"
"Z-2 LMP resembles a MP5 without the adjustable stock, the rear sight, has a reflex sight and a vertical foregrip. It has the word 'Z-2' right in front of its selective-fire switch. It has scratches, but most if not all the damage has been fixed with some patience.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <color_yellow>okay</color> and will <color_yellow>rarely malfunction</color> and <color_yellow>will handle some beating.</color>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"Z-2 LMP是一款由<info>Z-Arm Tech</info>生產的<info>小口徑</info>衝鋒槍，非常適合快速移動和機動。\n"
"Z-2 LMP類似於沒有可調槍托和後瞄準具的MP5，配有反射式瞄準鏡和垂直前握把。其快慢機開關正前方刻有“Z-2”字樣。槍身有劃痕，但大部分（即使不是全部）損傷已通過耐心修復。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<color_yellow>狀況尚可</color>，<color_yellow>很少發生故障</color>，並且<color_yellow>能承受一定磕碰</color>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模組內容</info>"

