msgstr "短點射"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "CM 530 BabyCOM"
msgid_plural "CM 530 BabyCOM"
msgstr[0] "CM 530 BabyCOM"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The CM 530 BabyCOMis a LMG produced by <info>critical mass</info>, \n"
"the CM 530 BabyCOM delivers a punishing rate of fire with incredible stopping power. A massive belt of rounds keeps it shooting harder, for longer. it also uses COM (Center Of Mass) technology to increase the bullet's speed and damage. this weapon has a bright LED on it's side and uses a cylindrical shaped drum magazine.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"CM 530 BabyCOM是由<info>臨界質量</info>生產的輕機槍，以驚人的停止威力提供懲罰性的射速。巨大的彈鏈使其能持續更長時間地猛烈射擊。它還使用COM（質心）技術來提高子彈速度和傷害。此武器側面有明亮的LED燈，並使用圓柱形彈鼓。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能優良</good>，<good>可能不會發生故障</good>，且<good>能承受相當程度的打擊</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模組內容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Hotspot"
msgid_plural "Hotspots"
msgstr[0] "熱點"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Hotspot uses intensified <info>microwave energy</info> to destroy organic targets easily, Although the Hotspot is a laser, it still has a range. Because of this, the laser beam can terminate in midair. it's produced by <info>Rancor</info>\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>unique</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"熱點使用強化的<info>微波能量</info>輕鬆摧毀有機目標。儘管熱點是激光武器，它仍有射程限制，因此激光束可能在半空中終止。它由<info>Rancor</info>生產。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>獨特</good>，<good>可能不會發生故障</good>，且<good>能承受相當程度的打擊</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模組內容</info>"

