#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Poison Claw"
msgid_plural "Poison Claws"
msgstr[0] "毒爪"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Poison Claw is one of the only pistol designed by Rancor \n"
"the weapon can be inspired by the look of the Vita-Saw from TF2n\n"
"it has a huge razor sharp blade under the weapon making it impossible to mount underbarrel accessories, and a small liquid tank on top covering the sights, the small liquid tank hold multiple liters of acid concentrated in an atomic shrinker enivoment, making for an effectively endless source of acid, the acid is then poured inside the bullet as you press the trigger to shoot off a bullet of concentrated acid inside of the enemy.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"毒爪是Rancor設計的少數手槍之一，其外觀可能受《軍團要塞2》中生命之鋸的啟發。武器下方有一把巨大的鋒利刀刃，使其無法安裝下掛配件，頂部有一個小液體罐覆蓋瞄準具。小液體罐在原子壓縮環境中儲存多升濃縮酸液，提供幾乎無限的酸液來源。扣動扳機時，酸液被注入子彈，向敵人射出濃縮酸彈。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能優良</good>，<good>可能不會發生故障</good>，且<good>能承受相當程度的打擊</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模組內容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Mixmaster"
msgid_plural "Mixmasters"
msgstr[0] "混音大師"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Mixmaster is an assault rifle produced by Rancor \n"
"it shoots super powered molted plasma from the air using battery power and has the unique ability to shoot two flechettes per trigger pull \n"
"This rifle is often designated as a crowd control gun thanks to the flechette, the metal weapon build is covered in metal spikes on top of it's red metal plates placed on top of the black metal frame.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"混音大師是Rancor生產的突擊步槍，利用電池能量從空氣中發射超強熔融等離子，並具有每次扣動扳機發射兩枚箭彈的獨特能力。由於箭彈特性，此步槍常被指定為人群控制武器。金屬武器結構上覆蓋金屬尖刺，紅色金屬板安裝在黑色金屬框架上。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能優良</good>，<good>可能不會發生故障</good>，且<good>能承受相當程度的打擊</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模組內容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Hard Thorn"
msgid_plural "Hard Thorns"
msgstr[0] "硬棘"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Hard Thorn is an assault rifle produced by Rancor \n"
"it shoots high caliber bullets, using super speed technology to burst the bullet in multiple shreds behaving like a shotgun with the same power and range of an assault rifle. \n"
"This rifle is often designated as a crowd control gun thanks to the high spread and range, the metal weapon build is covered in metal spikes on top of it's red metal plates placed on top of the black metal frame.\n"
"this weapon has a sharp blade with multiple spikes under it's barrel, making it impossible to attach underbarrel modifications but a very effective melee weapon.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"硬棘是Rancor生產的突擊步槍，發射大口徑子彈，利用超速技術使子彈爆裂成多塊碎片，行為類似霰彈槍，但具有突擊步槍的威力和射程。由於高擴散和射程，此步槍常被指定為人群控制武器。金屬武器結構上覆蓋金屬尖刺，紅色金屬板安裝在黑色金屬框架上。槍管下方有一把帶多個尖刺的鋒利刀刃，使其無法安裝下掛改裝件，但作為近戰武器非常有效。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能優良</good>，<good>可能不會發生故障</good>，且<good>能承受相當程度的打擊</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模組內容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Heartburn"
msgid_plural "Heartburns"
msgstr[0] "燒心"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Heartburn is an assault rifle manufactured by Rancor \n"
"the bullets fired from this weapon are molten before exiting the muzzle using high powered molten metal glowing on the sides of the barrel, this molten iron does not provide heat outside of the weapon's build\n"
" the metal weapon build is covered in metal spikes on top of it's red metal plates placed on top of the black metal frame, it has five razor sharp spikes under and above the barrel making it impossible to mount underbarrel modifications, also on the sides and on the front of the barrel there are bright red glowing lines and circles reminding you about it's unending molten power.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"燒心是Rancor製造的突擊步槍，發射的子彈在離開槍口前通過槍管側面高功率熔融金屬加熱而熔化，這種熔鐵不會在武器結構外散發熱量。金屬武器結構上覆蓋金屬尖刺，紅色金屬板安裝在黑色金屬框架上。槍管上下各有五根鋒利尖刺，使其無法安裝下掛改裝件。槍管側面和前方還有明亮的紅色發光線條和圓圈，提醒你其無盡的熔融力量。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能優良</good>，<good>可能不會發生故障</good>，且<good>能承受相當程度的打擊</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模組內容</info>"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid "Stripper"
msgid_plural "Strippers"
msgstr[0] "剝離者"

#: .\xeno_weapons.json
msgid ""
"the Stripper is a heavy automatic shotgun manufactured by Rancor, The Stripper is lever action like the 1887 Shockfield (even though the Stripper is still fully automatic, oddly enough)\n"
"the shotgun has a bayonet like blade under the barrel, but it's small enough so that it's possible to mount an underbarrel modification.\n"
"\n"
"This weapon is <good>good</good> and will <good>probably not malfunction</good> and <good>will handle quite the beating.</good>\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno's SAS4 Weapons pack Modded Content</info>"
msgstr ""
"剝離者是Rancor製造的重型自動霰彈槍，採用類似1887 Shockfield的槓桿動作（儘管剝離者仍然是全自動的，這很奇怪）。霰彈槍槍管下方有一把刺刀式刀刃，但足夠小，因此可以安裝下掛改裝件。\n"
"\n"
"此武器<good>性能優良</good>，<good>可能不會發生故障</good>，且<good>能承受相當程度的打擊</good>。\n"
"\n"
"<info>Xeno的SAS4武器包模組內容</info>"
